{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_015arjJaGGQs8AfZqBKgdDdb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the information I need to write the migration plan. Let me compile it:\n\n**Current State:**\n- Version: v24.1.0 (image: cockroachdb/cockroach:v24.1.0)\n- Cluster version setting: 24.1\n- 3 nodes, all live\n- TLS enabled (--certs-dir=/cockroach/cockroach-certs), secrets: cockroachdb-certs, cockroachdb-client-root, cockroachdb-node\n- StatefulSet: 3 replicas, Parallel pod management\n- Resources: 1 CPU, 2Gi memory (requests=limits)\n- Storage: 10Gi PVC per pod (ReadWriteOnce)\n- Cache: 25%, max-sql-memory: 25%\n- Services: headless (crdb-cluster) + public ClusterIP (crdb-cluster-public)\n- updateStrategy: RollingUpdate (partition: 0)\n\nI'm also noting the non-default cluster settings, including the internal cluster secret and diagnostics reporting configuration.\n\nLooking at the other custom settings: range merge is disabled (normally enabled), snapshot rebalance rate is set to 208 MiB versus the default 32 MiB, and the cluster version is 24.1. I need to verify whether diagnostics reporting actually defaults to true or false in this version, since it appeared in the non-default list from the query.\n\nFor zone configurations, the custom ones include a shorter garbage collection TTL of 4 hours on the default range instead of the standard 25 hours, and the system database is replicated 5 times for higher availability. I'm distinguishing between CockroachDB's built-in system defaults and the actual custom configurations here—the truly custom settings are the reduced garbage collection TTL on the default range and the explicit zone configs on those two user tables, while the system table overrides are just standard CRDB internals. Now I need to map out the migration strategy for the next minor version.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":504,"cache_read_input_tokens":33930,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":504},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"22f49c76-84a7-4910-8dde-86050f8037fc","uuid":"b1dba757-4165-4d79-91b9-249725372eee","request_id":"req_011CcLbzkh8ePnmBsLM84tNW"}
